'''Dricklefruit''' was a food item sold in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. In one variety, it came in jars. The [[Squib/Legends|Squib]] [[Momship]], ''[[Thrifty]]'', was decorated with mosaics made from such jars.

